## 🔧 Hardware Requirements

| Component | Specification |
|-----------|-------------|
| **Main Board** | ESP32-2432S032C (CYD) |
| **Display** | 3.2" TFT 320×240 Capacitive Touch |
| **Connection** | USB-C Cable |
| **Optional** | External antennas for extended range |

